          "username": "modesevenindustrialsolutions"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2022-11-30 13:42:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: -Code-Review\n\nShould the verify job and TOX file still be performing tests using Python 2.7? Could this potentially be removed, as you have to pin to extremely old and out-of-date Pythong modules if those are to pass.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
